headline: Heard on the Street Recap: Greenland Tensions Thaw

headline: Moderna (MRNA) Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of biotechnology company Moderna (NASDAQ:MRNA) jumped 8.8% in the afternoon session after the company, in partnership with Merck, announced positive results from a five-year follow-up study of their skin cancer vaccine.
